//    - pay_run schema → MIGRATED: 2 tables sang pay_mgmt, 7 tables sang pay_engine
//    - 2 NEW tables in pay_mgmt: pay_period, batch_approval
//    - 3 NEW tables in pay_engine: run_request, calculation_step, run_step,
//      cumulative_balance, element_dependency, input_source_config
//    - pay_bank.payment_batch, generated_file: FK updated pay_run.batch → pay_mgmt.batch
//    - Tổng: 8 new tables, 9 migrated tables, 2 FK updates
